column2: Passion Hits (Actual) count of matches in documents related to players displaying passion.
column3: Passion Hits (Normalised) normalied hits taking into account the total amount of content on each player, allows players to be compared.
column4: Passion Hits Positive ratio of hits relating to passion that used positive emotion.
column5: Passion Hits Negative ratio of hits relating to passion that used negative emotion.
column6: Crowd Hits (Actual) count of matchesi in documents mentioning player and crowd interaction.
column7: Crowd Hits (Normalised) normalied hits taking into account the total amount of content on each player, allows players to be compared.
column8: Crowd Supportive ratio of crowd-player interaction that used supportive emotion.
column9: Crowd Unsupportive ratio of crowd-player interaction that used unsupportive emotion.
column10: Crowd Sad ratio of crowd-player interaction that used sad emotion.
column11: Love Hits (Actual) count of matches in documents related to players describing love or fondness of Wimbledon.
column12: Love Hits (Normalised) normalied hits taking into account the total amount of content on each player, allows players to be compared.
column13: Personality Passion combination of emotional range and agreeableness, higher score means player has a more passionate personality.
column14: Personality Striving  a subfacet of conscientuousness, a high value indicates a player that sets high goals and works hard to achieve them.
column15: Personality Immoderation a subfacet of emotional range, a low value indicates a player who has control over their desires.
column16: Personality Anger a subfacet of emotional range, a high value indicates someone with a fiery temper.
column17: Personality Challenge Authority a subfacet of openess,  a player with a high value prefers to authority and traditional values to help bring about change.
column18: Passion Hits (Renormalied) passion hits normalised relative to the player with the most hits, gives a score between 0 and 1.
column19: Crowd Hits (Renormalised) crowd hits normalised relative to the player with the most hits, gives a score between 0 and 1.
column20: Love Hits (Renormalised) love hits normalised relative to the player with the most hits, gives a score between 0 and 1.
column21: Personality Passion (Renormalised) personality passion score normalised to the player with the largest value, gives a score between 0 and 1.
